a subtitle file in a calculator app.

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:16,500
In my defense, the file was named
"numbers.srt" - very misleading.

5
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:21,300
But then I discovered ConvertICO.com
and everything changed.

6
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:25,000
Now I convert subtitle formats
faster than I can misspell "entrepreneur."

7
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:29,800
This is my story.
This is The Subtitle Chronicles.

8
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:33,500
Chapter One: The Day Everything
Went Horribly Wrong.

9
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:37,400
It started with a phone call from the boss
at 6 AM on a Monday.

10
00:00:37,800 --> 00:00:41,000
Nothing good has ever started with
a phone call at 6 AM on a Monday.
